VybT0yMjAxMjYmdXRtX2NhbXBhaWduPW1vbmV5c3R1ZmY/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cB0729=
02a0" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" styl=
e=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-width:=
 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-=
color: #ccc;"> Bill Ackman=E2=80=99s big SPAC</a> is called Pershing Square=
 Tontine Holdings Ltd., and the =E2=80=9C<a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloom=
bergbusiness.com/click/26493398.266627/aHR0cHM6Ly9lbi53aWtpcGVkaWEub3JnL3dp=
a2kvVG9udGluZQ/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cB3c53eb98" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" it=
